**Gate 3 — Reference Inventory**

```json
{
  "question": "What reference images do you have for this shoot? Check all that apply.",
  "form": {
    "title": "Reference Inventory",
    "intro": "Select everything you have available. Leave unchecked if you don't have it.",
    "fields": [
      { "id": "product_ref", "label": "Product photo(s)", "type": "select", "options": ["Yes — I have product photos", "No"] },
      { "id": "model_ref", "label": "Model composite or face reference", "type": "select", "options": ["Yes — I have a model reference", "No"] },
      { "id": "setting_ref", "label": "Setting plate (already-generated background)", "type": "select", "options": ["Yes — I have a setting plate", "No"] },
      { "id": "style_ref", "label": "Style / visual reference (mood board, competitor ad, magazine spread)", "type": "select", "options": ["Yes — I have a style reference", "No"] },
      { "id": "none", "label": "None — text only, pure generation", "type": "select", "options": ["Yes — text only", "No"] }
    ],
    "submit_label": "Confirm references"
  }
}
```

I can work with commercial lingerie, swimwear, and fashion campaigns — that's standard brand content. Let me capture the full brief before generating.

A few quick clarifications to nail the 5-slide sequence:

```json
{
  "form": {
    "title": "5-Slide Model Carousel — Brief Details",
    "intro": "Each slide = a different model. Fill in what you know — I'll handle the creative direction.",
    "fields": [
      { "id": "brand_name", "label": "Brand name (for commercial intent signal)", "type": "text", "placeholder": "e.g. Lumière Swim, AURA Intimates, leave blank if undecided" },
      { "id": "model_diversity", "label": "Model diversity across slides", "type": "select", "options": ["All Korean women", "Mixed Asian ethnicities", "Diverse — different ethnicities per slide", "Director decides"] },
      { "id": "age_range", "label": "Age range across models", "type": "select", "options": ["18–24 (young adult)", "25–32 (mid adult)", "Mix of both", "Director decides"] },
      { "id": "wardrobe_style", "label": "Wardrobe tone across the 5 slides", "type": "select", "options": ["Luxury editorial — high-end fabrics, minimal detailing", "Playful resort — bright colors, tropical energy", "Dark moody — black lace, sheer panels, dramatic", "Mixed — each slide different wardrobe energy", "Director decides"] },
      { "id": "skin_tone_pref", "label": "Skin tone preference", "type": "select", "options": ["Fair to light (Fitzpatrick I–II)", "Light to medium (Fitzpatrick II–III)", "Medium to warm (Fitzpatrick III–IV)", "Director decides — varied across slides"] },
      { "id": "quality", "label": "Generation quality", "type": "select", "options": ["Medium — fast preview", "High — final production"] }
    ],
    "submit_label": "Build my 5-slide carousel"
  }
}
```
